    <item>
      <title>美国对朝鲜导弹和俄罗斯援助实施制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/us-issues-sanctions-related-to-north-korean-missiles-russia-aid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国财政部周一对 9 名个人和 7 个实体实施制裁，指控他们向朝鲜提供财政和军事支持，用于朝鲜弹道导弹计划和支持俄罗斯入侵乌克兰。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/us-issues-sanctions-related-to-north-korean-missiles-russia-aid</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 15:35:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国议会为二月提前选举扫清道路</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/german-parliament-clears-the-way-for-early-election-in-february</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国议会通过一项措施，为两个月后的全国大选铺平道路，支持总理奥拉夫·朔尔茨提前结束陷入困境的政府的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/german-parliament-clears-the-way-for-early-election-in-february</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 15:33:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>罗马尼亚新政府谈判在预算计划上遭遇首次阻碍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/talks-on-new-romanian-government-hit-first-snag-on-budget-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[罗马尼亚四个亲欧盟政党试图组建联合政府、平息政治动荡，但由于在削减欧盟最大预算赤字问题上存在分歧，这一尝试遭遇阻碍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/talks-on-new-romanian-government-hit-first-snag-on-budget-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 15:07:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大财政部长弗里兰因与特朗普闹矛盾突然辞职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/canadian-finance-minister-freeland-resigns-from-cabinet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大财政部长克里斯蒂亚·弗里兰（Chrystia Freeland）因在如何应对特朗普政府的问题上存在分歧而辞去总理贾斯汀·特鲁多内阁的职务，这一举动震惊政府。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/canadian-finance-minister-freeland-resigns-from-cabinet</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 14:23:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲盟友辩论敦促叙利亚统治者驱逐俄罗斯军队</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/russia-should-leave-syria-before-eu-sanctions-lifted-dutch-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，一些欧洲国家正考虑将俄罗斯军队驱逐出叙利亚作为解除对目前控制叙利亚大部分地区的伊斯兰组织的限制的先决条件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/russia-should-leave-syria-before-eu-sanctions-lifted-dutch-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 12:44:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
